These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: papayaade, 7up
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, papaya
1. the person drinking 7up is on the left or right of the person drinking papayaade##3
2. the person eating papaya is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1   |   2   |
| Beverage   | 7up  | papayaade |
| Food       | cauliflower | papaya |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, hot-chocolate
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rugby, soccer
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2   |
| Beverage   | juice | hot-chocolate |
| Sport      | soccer     | rugby  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-3::.
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
There are 2 different nationalities: dutch, italian
1. the dutch is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
2. the dutch is on the left or right of the person watching documentary movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |
| Movie-Genre   | action | documentary  |
| Nationality   | dutch | italian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-4::.
