.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-7::.
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, japanese
2 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit
1. the japanese is on the left or right of the chinese##3
2. the owner of the rabbit is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Nationality   | chinese | japanese |
| Pet           | rabbit     | goldfish  |

