.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-8::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: puzzles, camping
The people have 2 different jobs:  fisherman, writer
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
2. the writer is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is camping##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |
| Hobby   | camping | puzzles |
| Job     | fisherman        | writer |

