.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-12::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, surfing
The people use 2 different means of transport: skateboard, boat
1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2    |
| Sport       | volleyball  | surfing |
