.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-3-20::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: sudoku, puzzles
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: lacrosse, basketball
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby   | puzzles   | sudoku |
| Sport   | basketball | lacrosse   |

 